      "content": "exactly. it's just this constant, heavy weight. like, why should i have to spend my whole life fighting just to exist in a world that wasn't made for me? it's so much work just to stay afloat. sometimes i just wish i could stop fighting. i just want the noise to stop and to finally feel some kind of peace, even if it's not in this life.",
